import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import {
  Navbar,
  Login,
  Home,
  Err,
  Register,
  OtpVerify,
  Dashboard,
  Profile,
  Reset,
  Newnote,
  ForgotPassword,
  Verifyotp,
} from './components'

import './App.css'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar></Navbar>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path='/' component={Home} />

        <Route exact path='/register' component={Register} />
      </Switch>
    </>
    // </Router>
  )
}

export default App
